 squirrels.::Each chirp is a brief trill of three to five pulses.\";}i:297;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"298\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"298\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1\";i:2;s:8:\"astonish\";s:4:\"name\";s:8:\"astonish\";i:3;s:11:\"uh-ston-ish\";s:7:\"diction\";s:11:\"uh-ston-ish\";i:4;s:65:\"v. to fill with sudden and overpowering surprise or wonder; amaze\";s:11:\"description\";s:65:\"v. to fill with sudden and overpowering surprise or wonder; amaze\";i:5;s:169:\"To question that which seems to have ceased forever to astonish us.::They frighten a few people (mostly each other), are rude to bystanders and astonish a cleaning lady.\";s:8:\"examples\";s:169:\"To question that which seems to have ceased forever to astonish us.::They frighten a few people (mostly each other), are rude to bystanders and astonish a cleaning lady.\";}i:298;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"299\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"299\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1\";i:2;s:6:\"peruse\";s:4:\"name\";s:6:\"peruse\";i:3;s:8:\"puh-rooz\";s:7:\"diction\";s:8:\"puh-rooz\";i:4;s:77:\"v. to read through with thoroughness or care; to survey or examine in detail.\";s:11:\"description\";s:77:\"v. to read through with thoroughness or care; to survey or examine in detail.\";i:5;s:158:\"There are already 5081 photos to peruse, along with family stories and treasured recipes.::All of this information is available for you to peruse at any time.\";s:8:\"examples\";s:158:\"There are already 5081 photos to peruse, along with family stories and treasured recipes.::All of this information is available for you to peruse at any time.\";}i:299;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"300\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"300\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1\";i:2;s:9:\"anonymous\";s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"anonymous\";i:3;s:15:\"uh-non-uh-muh s\";s:7:\"diction\";s:15:\"uh-non-uh-muh s\";i:4;s:101:\"adj. of unknown name; whose name is withheld; lacking individuality, unique character, or distinction\";s:11:\"description\";s:101:\"adj. of unknown name; whose name is withheld; lacking ind