ion of dishonesty::His implication of immediate changes surprised us.\";}i:304;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"305\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"305\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1\";i:2;s:9:\"etiquette\";s:4:\"name\";s:9:\"etiquette\";i:3;s:8:\"et-i-kit\";s:7:\"diction\";s:8:\"et-i-kit\";i:4;s:146:\"n. the rules and conventions governing correct or polite behavior in society in general or in a specific social or professional group or situation\";s:11:\"description\";s:146:\"n. the rules and conventions governing correct or polite behavior in society in general or in a specific social or professional group or situation\";i:5;s:177:\"Yet blacks have a long history of manners, etiquette, dressing well.::She educates her customers about traditional sushi etiquette, using clever comparisons to southern manners.\";s:8:\"examples\";s:177:\"Yet blacks have a long history of manners, etiquette, dressing well.::She educates her customers about traditional sushi etiquette, using clever comparisons to southern manners.\";}i:305;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"306\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"306\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1\";i:2;s:11:\"proprietary\";s:4:\"name\";s:11:\"proprietary\";i:3;s:19:\"pruh-prahy-i-ter-ee\";s:7:\"diction\";s:19:\"pruh-prahy-i-ter-ee\";i:4;s:158:\"adj. relating to an owner, ownership, or something owned; privately owned and run; exhibiting characteristics that indicate ownership of somebody or something\";s:11:\"description\";s:158:\"adj. relating to an owner, ownership, or something owned; privately owned and run; exhibiting characteristics that indicate ownership of somebody or something\";i:5;s:133:\"For a business, that information would be proprietary.::Ending proprietary funding, end closed research results, restore peer review.\";s:8:\"examples\";s:133:\"For a business, that information would be proprietary.::Ending proprietary funding, end closed research results, restore peer review.\";}i:306;a:12:{i:0;s:3:\"307\";s:2:\"id\";s:3:\"307\";i:1;s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"category\";s:1:\"1